## Recommended Use
Use the versioned URL for stable, predictable behavior:
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kh57smth/adguard-allowlists/ (raw.githubusercontent.com in Bing)<VERSION>/allowlist.txt

Replace `<VERSION>` with the tag for this release.

